A shell-first AI agent

Usage: doit [COMMAND]

Commands:
  interactive  Start interactive REPL mode
  exit         Complete the current task and exit
  edit         Structured file editing
  exec         Execute a shell command via PTY
  glob         File pattern matching
  prompt       Block waiting for user input
  read         Read file contents with line numbers
  search       Search file contents with regex
  run          Execute a one-shot task (turn-by-turn display)
  task         Execute a task as sub-agent (non-interactive, result only)
  template     Generate prompt templates
  write        Write content to a file (reads from stdin)
  resume       Resume a previous session
  help         Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
